{"tid":598002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叫「結束一黨專政」影響參選立會？　梁耀忠指害怕　憂衝擊言論自由","createTime":"2018-03-19T06:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T14:32:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"acd5fc89611dde931f36080c1a742a0b441f5aff","tid":598002,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180319/s00001/6192a0ccd8b2a865a7d74baa3c6a04d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180319%2Fs00001%2F6192a0ccd8b2a865a7d74baa3c6a04d7.jpg&h=a1ac8566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大會議通過修改《憲法》後，新任人大常委、民建聯譚耀宗明言，以後叫「結束一黨專政」口號可能違反《憲法》及《基本法》，甚至影響參選立法會資格。支聯會常務秘書、街工立法會議員梁耀忠憂慮會影響香港言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n「結束一黨專政」是支聯會五大綱領之一，問到是否擔心影響參選立法會，梁耀忠向《明報》直言「當然會驚」，亦擔心影響香港言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n至於未來是否不再叫「結束一黨專政」，或支聯會會否改綱領等，他說要「重新考慮」，暫未能回答，惟重申「如果真是這樣做（影響參選立法會），會對香港言論自由帶來很大衝擊」。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗今早解釋，《憲法》修訂進一步肯定中國共產黨地位，把共產黨與中國特色社會主義連繫，故今後若有人提及「結束一黨專政」口號，可能牴觸《憲法》及《基本法》。他又說，具體能否參選，應交由選舉主任考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180319/s00001/1521441227764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180319%2Fs00001%2F1521441227764&d=oK81T%2BzW%2FRBjANvf%2FMit2UbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1ded288c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180319%2Fs00001%2F1521441227764&h=e95007d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180319/s00001/1521441227764</a>"},{"pid":"d31cac34c25da04abd2237bb8eda010508101ce0","tid":598002,"uid":47359,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"2016-2017年度立會傑出柒頭: 梁耀忠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/456906/5?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/456906/5?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"92f2fd40b8cbb02d34f3418b1b62331489aded01","tid":598002,"uid":35430,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"屌，依家又驚？食多兩個人血饅頭囉"},{"pid":"fb8444be69df0c4aef5e6b0ac7545ac4641566e6","tid":598002,"uid":14706,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"依條友正撚樣黎 比張好牌佢都唔識上"},{"pid":"9d6f23d4e15db1e07e5bf6bc79344efb3d329a26","tid":598002,"uid":15935,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"點解香港政壇可以咁撚on9?呢啲on9仔仲可以生存"},{"pid":"b48a4c8a703f8f616194bb1e0f43b6aed350fc74","tid":598002,"uid":38671,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:57:21.000Z","msg":"至於未來是否不再叫「結束一黨專政」，或支聯會會否改綱領等，他說要「重新考慮」，暫未能回答<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚇一嚇就唔要用左廿年既招牌，不如解散啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3d0e44a10e5f29394ab5e1058dfb26ef7a9955","tid":598002,"uid":38671,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"fb8444be69df0c4aef5e6b0ac7545ac4641566e6","tid":598002,"uid":14706,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:55:49.000Z","msg":"依條友正撚樣黎 比張好牌佢都唔識上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"俾佢做立法會主席都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43f28ee650d9a44a98126bd0f29bb2ac39e7115","tid":598002,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"夠啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好再出黎獻世啦"},{"pid":"effe0d31ef648273bd26f5ffd54293e1860293b6","tid":598002,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣就收皮啦<br />\n係人都睇到佢呢條白頭佬冇撚用啦或者寫好咗劇本要佢咁做"},{"pid":"a244ddffdb110a3479f1bb755f4644f640b07c3b","tid":598002,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:03:30.000Z","msg":"知驚？唔係呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd40dc6